OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,FThe head of the police force that
OL,7,Farrested Father Ted creator Graham
OL,8,FLinehan said his officers are in "an
OL,9,Fimpossible position" when dealing with
OL,10,Fstatements made online, and should not
OL,11,Fbe "policing toxic culture wars
OL,12,Fdebates".
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,15,FMark Rowley said he would make
OL,16,Fsuggestions to the Government about
OL,17,Fhow laws governing social media posts
OL,18,Fcould be changed, and is ready to test
OL,19,Fnew approaches "within a matter of
OL,20,Fweeks".
