OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,FIn his first statement after the
OL,7,Fcontroversy erupted, Sir Mark said:
OL,8,F"While the decision to investigate and
OL,9,Fultimately arrest the man was made
OL,10,Fwithin existing legislation, which
OL,11,Fdictates that a threat to punch
OL,12,Fsomeone from a protected group could
OL,13,Fbe an offence, I understand the
OL,14,Fconcern caused by such incidents given
OL,15,Fdiffering perspectives on the balance
OL,16,Fbetween free speech and the risks of
OL,17,Finciting violence in the real world.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
