OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,F"Most reasonable people would agree
OL,7,Fthat genuine threats of physical
OL,8,Fviolence against an identified person
OL,9,For group should be acted upon by
OL,10,Fofficers.
OL,12,F"Such actions can and do have serious
OL,13,Fand violent real-world implications.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
