OL,6,F"I don't believe we should be policing
OL,7,Ftoxic culture wars debates and
OL,8,Fofficers are currently in an
OL,9,Fimpossible position."
OL,11,FWriter Linehan was arrested at
OL,12,FHeathrow on Monday after flying in
OL,13,Ffrom Arizona, on suspicion of inciting
OL,14,Fviolence in posts on X.
OL,16,FHe said he was stopped by five armed
OL,17,Fpolice officers, although it is
OL,18,Funderstood this is because they were
OL,19,Ffrom the Met's Aviation unit and
OL,20,Froutinely carry firearms.
