OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,FAfter anger at his arrest Health
OL,7,FSecretary Wes Streeting suggested the
OL,8,FGovernment could look at legislation
OL,9,Fif the law is "not getting the balance
OL,10,Fright" on free speech.
OL,12,FIn his statement Sir Mark said: "I
OL,13,Fhave offered to provide suggestions to
OL,14,Fthe Home Office on where the law and
OL,15,Fpolicy should be clarified.
OL,17,F"Greater clarity and common sense
OL,18,Fwould enable us to limit the resources
OL,19,Fwe dedicate to tackling online
OL,20,Fstatements to those cases creating
OL,21,Freal threats in the real world.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@FO]tD@aOUyD@AOU
