OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,F"If agreed, we could be ready to test
OL,7,Fnew approaches quickly, within a
OL,8,Fmatter of weeks.
OL,10,F"As an immediate way of protecting our
OL,11,Fofficers from the situation we find
OL,12,Fourselves in today, we will be putting
OL,13,Fin place a more stringent triaging
OL,14,Fprocess to make sure only the most
OL,15,Fserious cases are taken forward in
OL,16,Ffuture ` where there is a clear risk
OL,17,Fof harm or disorder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
