OL,3,CPolice left 'between a rock and a hard
OL,4,Cplace' amid debate over Linehan arrest
OL,6,F"But officers across the country will
OL,7,Fhave to make similar decisions in
OL,8,Ffuture unless the law and guidance is
OL,9,Fchanged or clarified.
OL,11,F"I hope to see this happen without
OL,12,Fdelay so policing's focus can be
OL,13,Fsquarely on tackling priority issues
OL,14,Flike street crime and serious
OL,15,Fviolence."
OL,17,FOpposition politicians and Harry
OL,18,FPotter author JK Rowling are among
OL,19,Fthose who have criticised the arrest.
